stories.title: Heavy rain halts South Africa's winning run
stories.subTitle: South Africa v New Zealand, 4th ODI, Durban
stories.summary: Rain ruined the fourth one-day international in Durban, when the Kingsmead ground was saturated by heavy rain

stories.title: Nothing but pride at stake for New Zealand
stories.subTitle: South Africa v New Zealand, 4th ODI, Durban
stories.summary: New Zealand  will step onto Sahara Stadium, Durban with the five-match series already settled in the favour of South Africa, who took an unassailable 3-0 lead with victory in Port Elizabeth on Monday

stories.title: A double century of ODIs
stories.subTitle: South Africa v New Zealand, 4th ODI, Durban
stories.summary: Tomorrow's one-day international at Durban between New Zealand and South Africa will mark the 200th one-day match of Nathan Astle, the New Zealand batsman
